name: Fish Stew with Rouille
review: We love fish but no matter what I never found a perfect recipe breading,Fish Fry. Wow! Our next fish fry was so yummy!

name: Portuguese fish
review: First time trying this mix. Very tasty with both fish.I am really  liking how quick and easy it is to use

name: Cajun spiced fish tacos
review: Perfect fried fish every time! Crispy, golden, great flavor! I have used it on walleye, white bass, catfish and sauger!

name: Recheado Masala Fish
review: Delicious. I've gotta catch more fish now. Everybody loves this stuff. We  a fish fry for 80 people that fell through.

name: Saltfish and Ackee
review: We used it as a rub and as a batter. Dry rub was a little too crunchy for us. Seasoning doesn't overpower the fish flavor.

name: Three Fish Pie
review: Adds a little excellent flavor to all meats. I use it on fish, pork and chicken. Browns well. Sticks well to meat. A little sprinkle is all I use.
